   The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following general
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Sunday, Aug. 8 and thereafter. For questions about stories, please
contact Stew Slavin at the Daily News, (818) 713-3701.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-SEQUELS (Los Angeles) _Clint Eastwood as Batman? ``Pretty
in Pink 2?'' An ``Exorcist'' prequel? ``Beetlejuice Goes
Hawaiian?'' The rebirth of ``Tron''? Would you believe Rick Deckard
returning in 2018 to Los Angeles, which is turning into a desert,
to look for one more Nexus 6 replicant in ``Blade Runner 2''?
Welcome to the wacky world of sequel rumors, feuled by a
combination of anonymous tips from alleged insiders, pure
speculation and tantalyzing hints by stars, directors and
producers. By Dave McNary. (Will move in the ``e'' entertainment
and ``f'' financial news file.
</P>
