<P>
   &QL; 
MONTINI-COLUMN (Phoenix) _ The subject matter is of a mature
nature, so we've approached it as adults. Last week, married nurses
George and Tracy Miller, who operate an X-rated web site were fired
from their jobs at Scottsdale Healthcare Osborn. They say it's a
First Amendment issue. It's not. Quit being an grown-up for a
minute think of yourself in the fifth grade. If there was any thing
worse at that age than imagining your parents having sex, it would
be actually SEEING them have sex. By E.J. MONTINI. Story will move
in the ``A'' and ``K'' categories.
