girlfriend, but he's appealing the sentence on the grounds that the
two were living like husband and wife.In other words, Thomas
claims, it was really like raping his wife, which under Arizona law
is a minor offense. And at least one judge agrees with him. By
SUSIE STECKNER AND JODIE SNYDER. Move in `A' category.
